node.text: I witcha man in Miami and I had to stop by @lasermepleasemiami to get my facial and laser hair removal. Y’all I fell asleep getting my facial, IT WAS THAT GOOD! The best facial I have ever gotten and the laser hair removal was painless too! Make sure to come here whenever you’re in Miami they have so many services from IV hydration to facials, they do it ALL! Super professional as well!
